            "body": "The conversion from `unsigned char` to `bytes` assumes a zero-terminated array, which is fine for text strings but almost certainly nonsense for image data.\r\n\r\nI think if you do `cdef bytes as_bytes = data[:width*height*4]` this'll copy it into a `bytes` object of correct size, and it'll work.",
